data.description: $50,000 Price Improvement AND 2.75% assumable mortage for qualified buyers!! Welcome to a world of elegance, comfort, and boundless possibilities, as you step into this sprawling 6977 sq ft estate. Boasting 3 spacious bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warmth of beautiful red oak wood floors, which flow seamlessly throughout the home. The attention to detail is evident at every turn, with high-end finishes and meticulous craftsmanship throughout. Prepare to be spoiled in the 800 sq ft master closet, a haven for those who appreciate space and organization. The master suite itself is a sanctuary, providing the perfect escape from the daily hustle and bustle.  Call today.
